[18/12/2019 19:49:20] <font color="#ffff00">Billy  Sincolegas .</font>
[18/12/2019 19:49:23] <font color="#ffff00">Perfecta.</font>
[18/12/2019 19:49:27] <font color="#ffff00">Deja paso.</font>
